    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i dont want to go to the er if i dont have to... it's so expensive. plus i actually had a similar headache a few months ago and it went away after i took some ibuprofen and slept. maybe it's just stress? the drooping is really minor, i can still move my face, it just looks a bit off in the mirror. u sure it's not just a complex migraine?",
